name: CA State Treasurer
tweet: The bonds are designated as “Social Bonds” because they follow the Social Bond Principles adopted by the @ICMAgroup.

name: CA State Treasurer
tweet: Proceeds from the bond sale will be used by @California_HCD to assist in the production of permanent supportive housing for people who are experiencing homelessness, chronic homelessness or who are at risk of chronic homelessness, and who are in need of mental health services.

name: CA State Treasurer
tweet: CA Treasurer @FionaMa announced the sale of $1.05 billion in Social Bonds by @STO_CHFFA for the State’s No Place Like Home (NPLH) program to provide housing and assistance to the State’s homeless population.  Full press release available here:  https://t.co/EYSRLIqtbe
